  "detailed_description": "You play this turn-based, puzzle-like strategy game as a rabbit named \"Hop\". Your opponent is \"Skip\". The object of the game is to jump around on the game board, score points, and beat Skip.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/fbff77d7da8dbce9b050a8ae1a2c7749.poster.avif?t=1733414094\" width=536 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/fbff77d7da8dbce9b050a8ae1a2c7749.webm?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/fbff77d7da8dbce9b050a8ae1a2c7749.mp4?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Also on the board are playful creatures called “Thump\". Some move about randomly while others actively try to block your moves. <br>Beware the red Thump. If they touch you, you are thumped and lose a turn.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/7d0f30d3967b6c577ca933c3762d5d90.poster.avif?t=1733414094\" width=534 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/7d0f30d3967b6c577ca933c3762d5d90.webm?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/7d0f30d3967b6c577ca933c3762d5d90.mp4?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/b5fe084cbe1f65b53e2f822ddaff972d.poster.avif?t=1733414094\" width=538 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/b5fe084cbe1f65b53e2f822ddaff972d.webm?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/b5fe084cbe1f65b53e2f822ddaff972d.mp4?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To play well, you must account for Skip and the Thump sprites so that you avoid being blocked or forced into bad moves. And do not pass up the opportunity to earn the 10 bonus points when you meet a color objective.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/0ad54a025096dc1656065846c6c03a57.poster.avif?t=1733414094\" width=538 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/0ad54a025096dc1656065846c6c03a57.webm?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/0ad54a025096dc1656065846c6c03a57.mp4?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Whimsical Strategy-Puzzle game.  Fun for any age.<br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single player<br></li><li>100 levels of play<br></li><li>Good for long and short play-sessions alike<br></li><li>Family-Friendly<br></li><li>Deceptively tricky<br></li><li>No data are collected and stored outside of your device.<br></li><li>No ads. No microtransactions.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "You play this turn-based, puzzle-like strategy game as a rabbit named \"Hop\". Your opponent is \"Skip\". The object of the game is to jump around on the game board, score points, and beat Skip.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/fbff77d7da8dbce9b050a8ae1a2c7749.poster.avif?t=1733414094\" width=536 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/fbff77d7da8dbce9b050a8ae1a2c7749.webm?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/fbff77d7da8dbce9b050a8ae1a2c7749.mp4?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Also on the board are playful creatures called “Thump\". Some move about randomly while others actively try to block your moves. <br>Beware the red Thump. If they touch you, you are thumped and lose a turn.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/7d0f30d3967b6c577ca933c3762d5d90.poster.avif?t=1733414094\" width=534 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/7d0f30d3967b6c577ca933c3762d5d90.webm?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/7d0f30d3967b6c577ca933c3762d5d90.mp4?t=1733414094\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763350/extras/b5fe084cbe1f65b53e2f822ddaff972d.poster.avif?t=1733414094\" width=538 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/s